Description: Reads and writes INC files, a lightweight format that prepends
    INI-style metadata to a CSV file separated by '---' delimiters. Provides
    lightweight metadata schemas and validation. A thin layer over 'readr'
    that preserves ordinary CSV workflows while adding simple, human-readable
    metadata.
